Overview
===========
This is a project for Simple Ad Server based on play framwork. Main Functional Requirements are implemented. 

Instructions for running and deploying
=================================

- Make sure the version of your java is 1.8

- Install home-brew from http://brew.sh

- Install sbt from command line “brew install sbt”

- Download activator version 2.4.2 from https://www.playframework.com/download

- Install activator. Follow https://www.playframework.com/documentation/2.4.x/Installing

- Create new project from command line “vim .bash_profile”, “source .bash_profile”, “activator new”

- Choose 5) play-java when you see “Choose from these featured templates or enter a template name:
  1) minimal-akka-java-seed
  2) minimal-akka-scala-seed
  3) minimal-java
  4) minimal-scala
  5) play-java
  6) play-scala
  Then name your project

- Type command line “activator clean run” to run the project, then go to localhost:9000, you will see the welcome page   


